    "body": "Hey @Asahro,\r\n\r\nYou can use [`padding: 2`](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/widgets/pagination.html#struct-PaginationWidgetOptions-padding) in the widget options of pagination.\r\n\r\n```js\r\nsearch.addWidget(\r\n  instantsearch.widgets.pagination({ \r\n    padding: 2, \r\n  })\r\n);\r\n```",
